# 🧠 2. Rust module (motion detection)

## `Cargo.toml`

```toml
[package]
name = "motion"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[lib]
name = "motion"
crate-type = ["staticlib"]
```

---

## `lib.rs`

```rust
#[no_mangle]
pub extern "C" fn detect_motion(
    prev: *const u8,
    curr: *const u8,
    len: usize,
    threshold: u8,
) -> bool {
    let prev = unsafe { std::slice::from_raw_parts(prev, len) };
    let curr = unsafe { std::slice::from_raw_parts(curr, len) };

    let mut diff = 0;

    for i in 0..len {
        if (prev[i] as i16 - curr[i] as i16).abs() > threshold as i16 {
            diff += 1;
        }
    }

    diff > len / 20 // 5% threshold
}
```

👉 уже выглядит как **реальный embedded Rust**

---

