# 🎥 1. GStreamer (реальный pipeline)

## Установка

```bash
sudo apt install -y \
  gstreamer1.0-tools \
  gstreamer1.0-plugins-base \
  gstreamer1.0-plugins-good \
  gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad \
  gstreamer1.0-libav
```

---

## 🔥 Pipeline (основа)

```bash
gst-launch-1.0 v4l2src device=/dev/video0 ! \
  videoconvert ! x264enc bitrate=2048 ! \
  rtph264pay ! udpsink host=127.0.0.1 port=5000
```

---

## C++ интеграция

### `gstreamer_pipeline.hpp`

```cpp
#pragma once
#include <gst/gst.h>
#include <string>

class GstPipeline {
public:
    bool init(const std::string& pipeline_str);
    void start();
    void stop();

private:
    GstElement* pipeline = nullptr;
};
```

---

### `gstreamer_pipeline.cpp`

```cpp
#include "gstreamer_pipeline.hpp"
#include <iostream>

bool GstPipeline::init(const std::string& pipeline_str) {
    gst_init(nullptr, nullptr);

    GError* error = nullptr;
    pipeline = gst_parse_launch(pipeline_str.c_str(), &error);

    if (!pipeline) {
        std::cerr << "GStreamer error: " << error->message << std::endl;
        return false;
    }
    return true;
}

void GstPipeline::start() {
    gst_element_set_state(pipeline, GST_STATE_PLAYING);
}

void GstPipeline::stop() {
    gst_element_set_state(pipeline, GST_STATE_NULL);
}
```

---

## 🎯 Production pipeline (используй)

```cpp
std::string pipeline =
  "v4l2src device=/dev/video0 ! videoconvert ! "
  "x264enc bitrate=2048 speed-preset=ultrafast ! "
  "tee name=t "
  "t. ! queue ! appsink name=appsink "
  "t. ! queue ! rtph264pay ! udpsink host=127.0.0.1 port=5000";
```

👉 `appsink` → отдаёт фреймы в Rust

---

# 🌐 2. Реальный REST API

Используем: **cpp-httplib**

## подключение

```bash
git submodule add https://github.com/yhirose/cpp-httplib.git external/httplib
```

---

## `http_server.cpp`

```cpp
#include "httplib.h"
#include <atomic>

std::atomic<int> motion_events = 0;

void start_server() {
    httplib::Server svr;

    svr.Get("/health", [](auto&, auto& res) {
        res.set_content("{\"status\":\"ok\"}", "application/json");
    });

    svr.Get("/metrics", [](auto&, auto& res) {
        res.set_content(
            "{\"motion_events\":" + std::to_string(motion_events.load()) + "}",
            "application/json"
        );
    });

    svr.listen("0.0.0.0", 8080);
}
```

---

## 🔥 интеграция с main

```cpp
if (motion) {
    motion_events++;
}
```

