# 🎥 1. WebRTC real-time stream

## Стек:

* GStreamer + `webrtcbin`
* Browser client (`<video>` HTML5)

---

### C++ GStreamer WebRTC pipeline

```cpp id="webrtc1"
std::string pipeline =
  "v4l2src device=/dev/video0 ! videoconvert ! queue ! x264enc bitrate=2000 speed-preset=ultrafast tune=zerolatency ! "
  "rtph264pay config-interval=1 pt=96 ! application/x-rtp,media=video,encoding-name=H264,payload=96 ! "
  "webrtcbin name=sendrecv stun-server=stun://stun.l.google.com:19302";
```

* `webrtcbin` сам генерирует SDP
* Передаем SDP через REST API
* Browser получает live поток (HTML `<video>`)

---

### Browser HTML

```html
<video id="video" autoplay playsinline></video>
<script>
const pc = new RTCPeerConnection();
pc.ontrack = event => document.getElementById("video").srcObject = event.streams[0];

// fetch SDP from C++ / REST API
// send local SDP back
</script>
```

